---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Us - RailDevHub" description="Learn about the RailDevHub team and our mission to transform railway technology">
  <Header />

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-32 pb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 via-white to-blue-50 dark:from-gray-900 dark:via-gray-800 dark:to-gray-900 transition-colors duration-200">
    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-display font-bold text-railway-steel dark:text-white mb-6">
          About RailDevHub
        </h1>
        <p class="text-2xl text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 font-semibold mb-4">
          Where Steel Rails Meet Silicon Dreams
        </p>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          We are a specialized team of 15 visionaries who believe that the future of transportation is being written in code, analyzed by AI, and powered by data streaming through thousands of kilometers of steel rails.
        </p>
        <div class="inline-block bg-white/80 dark:bg-gray-800/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg">
          <p class="text-lg italic text-railway-steel dark:text-gray-200">
            "Every train that crosses Turkey carries not just passengers, but our dreams of a smarter, safer, and more connected future."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Origin Story Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 transition-colors duration-200">
    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-railway-steel dark:text-white mb-6">
            Our Story: The Birth of a Revolution
          </h2>
          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-primary-700 dark:from-primary-700 dark:to-primary-800 rounded-2xl p-8 text-white mb-8">
              <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed mb-4">
                It started with a simple question: <strong>"What if we could see the future of every train before it departs?"</strong>
              </p>
              <p class="text-lg text-primary-100 dark:text-primary-200 leading-relaxed">
                In a small office in Istanbul, overlooking the Bosphorus where continents meet, 15 engineers, data scientists, and railway enthusiasts gathered. They shared a vision that seemed impossible: to transform Turkey's vast railway network into the world's smartest, most efficient transportation system.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 my-12">
              <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-8">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-railway-steel dark:text-white mb-4">üöÇ The Railway Heritage</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                  Some of us grew up next to train stations, falling asleep to the rhythmic sound of wheels on tracks. Others were engineers who spent years maintaining locomotives. We all shared one thing: a deep love for railways and a frustration with outdated systems.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-8">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-railway-steel dark:text-white mb-4">üí° The Digital Awakening</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                  We witnessed how AI transformed industries‚Äîfrom healthcare to finance. Yet railways, the backbone of nations, still relied on paper forms and manual processes. We knew we had to change this.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-railway-steel dark:text-white mb-6">
            Our Mission: Rewriting the Future of Mobility
